message: Prior version made it sound like I only won ONE Emmy...In SLC.  Truth be told, I've WON 13 Emmy Awards in multiple markets.
added a space between a bracket and the word "at"
added a space after a word
I deleted things that are not true that have been written about me.
Added documentary work to career.  Added companies founded
is a documentary filmmaker.  not WAS
removed GAY in reference to me.  I am a journalist.  My sexuality has nothing to do with my journalism
added two companies created by Cowan

Factual adjustments on this page which is about myself.  I don't like being called a gay journalist anymore than a black journalist wants their race put in front of their profession.  I'm a journalist.  Period.
I removed, once again, references to me being a gay journalist.  See blog post at http://reeddrc.blogspot.com/
added yoga and meditation teacher with citation
Changes made Referencing a recent blog post by Cowan at: http://reeddrc.blogspot.com/2017/05/wikipedia-clarifications.html
